8dea5be5170ce67bf9f45fbe3d25eb4828a77a5a.query:
SELECT alert_rules.name, enabled_destinations.alert_id, destinations.type as "type: _" FROM enabled_destinations
JOIN destinations ON enabled_destinations.destination_id = destinations.id
JOIN alert_rules ON enabled_destinations.alert_id = alert_rules.id
WHERE destinations.active = true
    AND enabled_destinations.alert_id = $1
